### ================================================================
### NestJS RabbitMQ Microservices - API Testing
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension:
### https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=humao.rest-client
### ================================================================

### --------------------------------------------------
### 1. Health Check
### Tests: Nginx → API Gateway connectivity
### --------------------------------------------------
GET http://localhost:3000/orders/health

### --------------------------------------------------
### 2. Create Order - Basic
### Tests: Full event flow (Order → Payment → Notification)
### --------------------------------------------------
POST http://localhost:3000/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "cust-001",
  "productName": "Widget-X",
  "quantity": 2,
  "amount": 99.99
}

### --------------------------------------------------
### 3. Create Order - With Notes (optional field)
### --------------------------------------------------
POST http://localhost:3000/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "cust-002",
  "productName": "Gadget-Y",
  "quantity": 1,
  "amount": 49.50,
  "notes": "Gift wrap please"
}

### --------------------------------------------------
### 4. Create Order - High Value
### --------------------------------------------------
POST http://localhost:3000/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "cust-003",
  "productName": "Enterprise-Server",
  "quantity": 5,
  "amount": 15000.00
}

### --------------------------------------------------
### 5. Error Case - Missing Required Field (productName)
### Expected: 400 Bad Request
### --------------------------------------------------
POST http://localhost:3000/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "cust-004",
  "quantity": 1,
  "amount": 10.00
}

### --------------------------------------------------
### 6. Error Case - Invalid Quantity (min: 1)
### Expected: 400 Bad Request
### --------------------------------------------------
POST http://localhost:3000/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "cust-005",
  "productName": "Widget",
  "quantity": 0,
  "amount": 10.00
}

### --------------------------------------------------
### 7. Error Case - Invalid Amount (min: 0)
### Expected: 400 Bad Request
### --------------------------------------------------
POST http://localhost:3000/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "cust-006",
  "productName": "Widget",
  "quantity": 1,
  "amount": -5.00
}

### ================================================================
### 8. Public Query Endpoints (Read data from MongoDB via API Gateway)
### ================================================================

### --------------------------------------------------
### 8a. Stats Dashboard - Document counts + health check
### --------------------------------------------------
GET http://localhost:3000/stats

### --------------------------------------------------
### 8b. Load Balance Info - Instance ID + uptime
### --------------------------------------------------
GET http://localhost:3000/load-balance/info

### --------------------------------------------------
### 8c. List All Orders (with serving instance)
### --------------------------------------------------
GET http://localhost:3000/orders

### --------------------------------------------------
### 8d. Get Order by ID (replace <orderId> with actual ID)
### --------------------------------------------------
GET http://localhost:3000/orders/<orderId>

### --------------------------------------------------
### 8e. Get Payment for an Order (replace <orderId>)
### --------------------------------------------------
GET http://localhost:3000/orders/<orderId>/payment

### --------------------------------------------------
### 8f. Get Notifications for an Order (replace <orderId>)
### --------------------------------------------------
GET http://localhost:3000/orders/<orderId>/notifications

### --------------------------------------------------
### 8g. List All Payments
### --------------------------------------------------
GET http://localhost:3000/payments

### --------------------------------------------------
### 8h. List All Notifications
### --------------------------------------------------
GET http://localhost:3000/notifications

